#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:2
msgid "Unicode"
msgstr "Unicode"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:5
msgid "基本概念"
msgstr "Basic Concepts"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:8
msgid "BMP"
msgstr "BMP"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:9
msgid "BMP (Basic Multilingual Plane)，译作基本多文种平面，是Unicode中的一个编码区块。"
msgstr ""
"BMP (Basic Multilingual Plane) is a Unicode encoding block."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:12
msgid "码平面"
msgstr "Plane"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:13
msgid "Unicode编码点分为17个平面（plane），每个平面包含2^16（即65536）个码位。17个平面的码位可表示为从U+xx0000到U+xxFFFF，其中xx表示十六进制值从0016到1016，共计17个平面。"
msgstr ""
"Unicode code points are divided into 17 planes. Each plane contains 2^16 "
"(65536) code points. The code points in these 17 planes can be represented "
"from U+xx0000 to U+xxFFFF, where xx is the hexadecimal value from 00 to 10."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:16
msgid "Code Point"
msgstr "Code Point"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:17
msgid "Code Point也被称作Code Position，译作码位或编码位置，是指组成代码空间的数值。"
msgstr ""
"A Code Point, also called a Code Position, is a numeric value in the code "
"space."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:20
msgid "Code Unit"
msgstr "Code Unit"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:21
msgid ""
"指某种 Unicode 编码方式里编码一个 Code Point 需要的最少字节数，比如 UTF-8 需要最少一个字节，UTF-16 "
"最少两个字节，UCS-2 两个字节，UCS-4 和 UTF-32 四个字节。"
msgstr ""
"The minimum number of bytes required to encode a Code Point in a particular "
"Unicode encoding. For example, UTF-8 requires at least one byte, UTF-16 "
"requires at least two bytes, UCS-2 uses two bytes, and UCS-4 and UTF-32 use "
"four bytes."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:24
msgid "Surrogate Pair"
msgstr "Surrogate Pair"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:25
msgid ""
"Surrogate Pair 是用于 UTF-16 的以向后兼容 UCS-2 的，做法是取 UCS-2 范围里的 0xD800~0xDBFF "
"(称为 high surrogates) 和 0xDC00~0xDFFF (称为 low surrogates) 的码位，一个 high "
"surrogate 接一个 low surrogate 拼成四个字节表示超出 BMP 的字符，两个 surrogate range 都是 1024"
" 个码位，所以 surrogate pair 可以表达 1024 x 1024 = 1048576 = 0x100000 个字符。"
msgstr ""
"A Surrogate Pair is used by UTF-16 for backward compatibility with UCS-2. "
"It takes code points in the UCS-2 ranges 0xD800~0xDBFF (called high "
"surrogates) and 0xDC00~0xDFFF (called low surrogates). A high surrogate "
"followed by a low surrogate forms four bytes that represent a character "
"outside the BMP. Each surrogate range contains 1024 code points, so a "
"surrogate pair can express 1024 x 1024 = 1048576 = 0x100000 characters."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:28
msgid "Combining Character"
msgstr "Combining Character"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:29
msgid "例如 ``He̊llö`` 含有重音符号之类的字符，进行组合会使用大量的码位。所以这种字符多用组合的方式来实现。"
msgstr ""
"For example, ``He̊llö`` contains characters such as accent marks. Composition "
"can use many code points, so these characters are often implemented through "
"combining sequences."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:32
msgid "BOM"
msgstr "BOM"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:33
msgid ""
"字节顺序标记（byte-order mark，BOM）是一个有特殊含义的统一码字符，码点为 ``U+FEFF`` 。当以UTF-16或UTF-"
"32来将UCS字符所组成的字符串编码时，这个字符被用来标示其字节序。常被用于区分是否为UTF编码。"
msgstr ""
"The byte-order mark (BOM) is a Unicode character with special meaning. Its "
"code point is ``U+FEFF``. When a string made of UCS characters is encoded as "
"UTF-16 or UTF-32, this character is used to indicate byte order. It is often "
"used to distinguish whether content uses a UTF encoding."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:36
msgid "编码方式"
msgstr "Encoding Forms"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:39
msgid "UCS-2"
msgstr "UCS-2"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:40
msgid ""
"UCS-2 (2-byte Universal Character "
"Set)是一种定长的编码方式，UCS-2仅仅简单的使用一个16位码元来表示码位，也就是说编码范围在0到0xFFFF的码位范围内。"
msgstr ""
"UCS-2 (2-byte Universal Character Set) is a fixed-length encoding. UCS-2 "
"simply uses one 16-bit code unit to represent a code point, so its encoding "
"range covers code points from 0 to 0xFFFF."

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:43
msgid "UTF-8"
msgstr "UTF-8"

#: ../../source/misc/unicode.rst:44
msgid ""
"UTF-8（8-bit Unicode Transformation "
"Format）是一种针对Unicode的可变长度字符编码，也是一种前缀码。它可以用一至四个字节对Unicode字符集中的所有有效编码点进行编码，属于Unicode标准的一部分。编码方式如下"
msgstr ""
"UTF-8 (8-bit Unicode Transformation Format) is a variable-length character "
"encoding for Unicode and is also a prefix code. It can encode all valid code "
"points in the Unicode character set using one to four bytes, and it is part "
"of the Unicode standard. The encoding form is as follows."

